name: Jean Clutch | Peacock Green
description:
The new Jean clutch from nawá is a re-collection of one of the most famous beauties of the 1960’s: Jean Shrimpton.

The clutch is refined and carefree, epitomized by the fashion icon’s avant-garde looks.

The fun mixture and contrast between the smooth surface of the nappa leather and the textured sweet water snake leather will make you want to own each of the many colors the clutch comes in.

The new nawá clutch is a story of a personality, a fashion icon of the swinging London,and of fine craftsmanship: handmade gold plated fermoir and thought after detailing, add to the value of the little piece of art.

Size/dimensions
12.5cm x 17cm x 5cm

name: Tree of Life | Sunshine Yellow Leather
description:
Tree of Life, is a luxurious top quality fashion handbag, and nawa's first creation

Taking inspiration from the “Tree of Life”, a beautiful and mystical concept reflecting the connection of all forms of creation, this retro-chic leather and embroidered jute handbag is a luxe redesign of iconic styles of the 1950’s.

With its gold plated chain, gold plated logo and rich colored interior, it is the perfect balance of edge and elegance, retro and modern.

Meticulously crafted in carefully selected leather and delicately embroidered, small wrinkles and imperfections prove its naturalness, rendering each piece one of a kind. to preserve its original beauty, take good care of your newly purchased item.

name: Hanami  Messenger Bag | Lavender Color
description:
Hanami refers to the Japanese custom of enjoying the beauty of flowers, and more precisely the Sakura flower or the cherry blossoms as they only blossom a week or two. 

This leather Messenger shoulder bag sends us back in time with its classic details, hand crocheted flower pattern silk and modern twist shape. The detachable strap lets you swing your things over your shoulder or just hold on to it for a night out.

From the subtle gold plated buckle and gold plated accents to the sturdy contrasted lining and inner pocket, It will secure both your trusty belongings and your trendsetter status.

name: Canna | Duke Blue and Silver vintage look
description:
The “Canna” collection is inspired by the beautiful and colorful Canna lilies that grow tall and high with their vibrant colors. It’s the happy 60’s with their bright retro glamour re-invented. 

The oversized clutch, a colored nappa-leather version, re-visits the vintage look to give it an edgy sophistication: a contrasting hand crocheted flower pattern silk is elegantly farmed by the natural leather and a vintage inspired fermoire, with plenty of space inside to fit all your items.
